Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libssl3 | libssl1.1
Suggests: jq
Description: AI-powered CLI tool with multiple provider support
 echomind is a lightweight, fast command-line tool written in Rust that
 pipes input to AI chat APIs and outputs responses.
 .
 Features:
  - Multiple API provider support (chat, chatanywhere, openai, claude, ollama)
  - Interactive REPL mode for multi-turn conversations
  - Streaming responses with real-time display
  - Configuration system with TOML support
  - Progress indicators and colored output
  - Coder mode for clean code generation
